erland]].\n\n==Career statistics==\n\n===Club===\n''Updated to end of 2018 season''.<ref>Nippon Sports Kikaku Publishing inc./\u65e5\u672c\u30b9\u30dd\u30fc\u30c4\u4f01\u753b\u51fa\u7248\u793e, [https://www.amazon.co.jp/J1-J3%E9%81%B8%E6%89%8B%E5%90%8D%E9%91%91%E3%83%8F%E3%83%B3%E3%83%87%E3%82%A3%E7%89%88-2018-NSK-MOOK/dp/4905411521 \"J1&J2&J3\u9078\u624b\u540d\u9451\u30cf\u30f3\u30c7\u30a3\u7248 2018 (NSK MOOK)\"], 7 February 2018, Japan, {{ISBN|978-4905411529}} (p. 92 out of 289)</ref><ref>Nippon Sports Kikaku Publishing inc./\u65e5\u672c\u30b9\u30dd\u30fc\u30c4\u4f01\u753b\u51fa\u7248\u793e, [https://www.amazon.co.jp/2017-J1-J3%E9%81%B8%E6%89%8B%E5%90%8D%E9%91%91-NSK-MOOK/dp/4905411424/ref=pd_sim_14_1/356-9491148-0114816?_encoding=UTF8&psc=1&refRID=BA8BN4Y0F97GNWKQM78H \"2017 J1&J2&J3\u9078\u624b\u540d\u9451 (NSK MOOK)\"], 8 February 2017, Japan, {{ISBN|978-4905411420}} (p. 52 out of 289)</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Club\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Season\n!colspan=\"2\"|League\n!colspan=\"2\"|Cup<sup>[[#notes gs1|1]]</sup>\n!colspan=\"2\"|League Cup<sup>[[#notes gs2|2]]</sup>\n!colspan=\"2\"|Asia<sup>[[#notes gs3|3]]</sup>\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n|-\n!Apps\n!Goals\n!Apps\n!Goals\n!Apps\n!Goals\n!Apps\n!Goals\n!Apps\n!Goals\n|-\n|rowspan=\"7\"|[[Kyoto Sanga FC]]\n|[[2008 J. League Division 1|2008]]\n|2||0||1||0||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|-||3||0\n|-\n|[[2009 J. League Division 1|2009]]\n|2||0||1||1||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|-||3||1\n|-\n|[[2010 J. League Division 1|2010]]\n|14||3||0||0||5||1||colspan=\"2\"|-||19||4\n|-\n|[[2011 J. League Division 2|2011]]\n|27||7||6||5||colspan=\"2\"|-||colspan=\"2\"|-||33||12\n|-\n|[[2012 J. League Division 2|2012]]\n|39||11||2||0||colspan=\"2\"|-||colspan=\"2\"|-||41||11\n|-\n|[[2013 J. League Division 2|2013]]\n|18||3||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|-||colspan=\"2\"|-||18||3\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[2014 J. League Division 2|2014]]\n|4||0||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|-||colspan=\"2\"|-||4||0\n|-\n|[[Kataller Toyama]]\n|16