{"title_page": "Takuma Takeda", "text_new": "{{Infobox football biography\n|name=Takuma Takeda<br/>\u6b66\u7530 \u62d3\u771f\n|image=\n|image_size=\n|caption=\n|fullname=Takuma Takeda\n|birth_date={{Birth date and age|1995|10|12}}\n|birth_place=[[Wakayama Prefecture|Wakayama]], [[Japan]]\n|death_date=\n|death_place=\n|height={{Height|m=1.70}}\n|position=[[Forward (association football)|Forward]]\n|currentclub=[[Fagiano Okayama]]\n|clubnumber=30\n|youthyears1= |youthclubs1=Nanki SC<ref name=foot/>\n|youthyears2= |youthclubs2=Kaohsiung MS<ref name=foot/>\n|youthyears3= |youthclubs3=Chuo Gakuin HS<ref name=foot/>\n|youthyears4=2014\u20132017|youthclubs4=[[Tokai Gakuen University]]\n|years1=2018\u2013|clubs1=[[Fagiano Okayama]]|caps1=1|goals1=0\n|totalcaps=1|totalgoals=0\n|nationalyears1=|nationalteam1=|nationalcaps1=|nationalgoals1=\n|manageryears1=|managerclubs1=\n|medaltemplates=\n|club-update= 31 December 2018\n|nationalteam-update=\n}}\n{{Nihongo|'''Takuma Takeda'''|\u6b66\u7530 \u62d3\u771f|Takeda Takuma|born October 12, 1995}} is a [[Japan]]ese [[Association football|football]] player.<ref>{{J.League player}}</ref>\n\n==Playing career==\nTakeda was born in [[Wakayama Prefecture]] on October 12, 1995. After graduating from [[Tokai Gakuen University]], he joined [[J2 League]] club [[Fagiano Okayama]] in 2018. His contract got extended in December 2018.<ref name=foot>[http://www.fagiano-okayama.com/news/p1473054463.html \u5951\u7d04\u66f4\u65b0\u9078\u624b\u306e\u304a\u77e5\u3089\u305b], fagiano-okayama.com, 7 December 2018</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{J.League player}}\n\n{{Fagiano Okayama squad}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Takeda, Takuma}}\n[[Category:1995 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Tokai Gakuen University alumni]]\n[[Category:Association football people from Wakayama Prefecture]]\n[[Category:Japanese footballers]]\n[[Category:J2 League players]]\n[[Category:Fagiano Okayama players]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n\n\n{{Japan-footy-forward-1990s-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football biography\n|name=Takuma Takeda<br/>\u6b66\u7530 \u62d3\u771f\n|image=\n|image_size=\n|caption=\n|fullname=Takuma Takeda\n|birth_date={{Birth date and age|1995|10|12}}\n|birth_place=[[Wakayama Prefecture|Wakayama]], [[Japan]]\n|death_date=\n|death_place=\n|height={{Height|m=1.70}}\n|position=[[Forward (association football)|Forward]]\n|currentclub=[[Fagiano Okayama]]\n|clubnumber=30\n|youthyears1= |youthclubs1=Nanki SC<ref name=foot/>\n|youthyears2= |youthclubs2=Kaohsiung MS<ref name=foot/>\n|youthyears3= |youthclubs3=Chuo Gakuin HS<ref name=foot/>\n|youthyears4=2014\u20132017|youthclubs4=[[Tokai Gakuen University]]\n|years1=2018\u2013|clubs1=[[Fagiano Okayama]]|caps1=1|goals1=0\n|totalcaps=1|totalgoals=0\n|nationalyears1=|nationalteam1=|nationalcaps1=|nationalgoals1=\n|manageryears1=|managerclubs1=\n|medaltemplates=\n|club-update= 31 December 2018\n|nationalteam-update=\n}}\n{{Nihongo|'''Takuma Takeda'''|\u6b66\u7530 \u62d3\u771f|Takeda Takuma|born October 12, 1995}} is a [[Japan]]ese [[Association football|football]] player.<ref>{{J.League player}}</ref>\n\n==Playing career==\nTakeda was born in [[Wakayama Prefecture]] on October 12, 1995. After graduating from [[Tokai Gakuen University]], he joined [[J2 League]] club [[Fagiano Okayama]] in 2018. His contract got extended in December 2018.<ref name=foot>[http://www.fagiano-okayama.com/news/p1473054463.html \u5951\u7d04\u66f4\u65b0\u9078\u624b\u306e\u304a\u77e5\u3089\u305b], fagiano-okayama.com, 7 December 2018</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{J.League player}}\n\n{{Fagiano Okayama squad}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Takeda, Takuma}}\n[[Category:1995 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Tokai Gakuen University alumni]]\n[[Category:Association football people from Wakayama Prefecture]]\n[[Category:Japanese footballers]]\n[[Category:J2 League players]]\n[[Category:Fagiano Okayama players]]\n[[Category:As