{"title_page": "Takuma Nishimura (footballer)", "text_new": "{{Infobox football biography\n|name=Takuma Nishimura <br> \u897f\u6751 \u62d3\u771f\n|image= Takuma Nishimura 2018.jpg\n|image_size=\n|alt=\n|caption=\n|fullname=Takuma Nishimura\n|birth_date={{Birth date and age|1996|10|22}}\n|birth_place=[[Nagoya]], [[Aichi Prefecture|Aichi]], [[Japan]]\n|height={{Height|m=1.78}}\n|position=[[Forward (association football)|Forward]]\n|currentclub=[[Portimonense S.C.|Portimonense]]\n|clubnumber=30\n| youthyears1 = 2012\u20132014 | youthclubs1 = Toyama First High School\n|years1 = 2015\u20132018 |clubs1 = [[Vegalta Sendai]]                                  | caps1 = 64 | goals1 = 14\n|years2 = 2015      |clubs2 = \u2192 [[J.League U-22 Selection|J. League U-22]] (loan) | caps2 = 14 | goals2 =  1\n|years3 = 2018\u2013     |clubs3 = [[PFC CSKA Moscow|CSKA Moscow]]                     | caps3 = 17 | goals3 =  2\n|years4 = 2020\u2013     |clubs4 = \u2192 [[Portimonense S.C.|Portimonense]] (loan)         | caps4 =  2 | goals4 =  0\n|years5 = 2020\u2013     |clubs5 = \u2192 [[Vegalta Sendai]] (loan)| caps5 =  0 | goals5 =  0\n|medaltemplates=\n{{Medal|Team|[[Vegalta Sendai]]}}\n{{Medal|RU|[[Emperor's Cup]]|[[2018 Emperor's Cup|2018]]}}\n|club-update= 26 January 2020\n}}\n\n{{Nihongo|'''Takuma Nishimura'''|\u897f\u6751 \u62d3\u771f|Nishimura Takuma|born October 22, 1996}} is a [[Japan]]ese [[Association football|football]] player.<ref>[https://data.j-league.or.jp/SFIX04/?player_id=15808 J.League Data Site]{{in lang|ja}}</ref> He plays for Japanese club [[Vegalta Sendai]] on loan from the Russian club [[PFC CSKA Moscow]].\n\n==Club career==\nOn 31 August 2018, he signed a 4-year contract with the [[Russian Premier League]] club [[PFC CSKA Moscow|CSKA Moscow]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[PFC CSKA Moscow]]|url=https://pfc-cska.com/novosti/vse-novosti/novosti-osnovy/takuma-nishimura-v-pfk-cska/|title=\u0422\u0430\u043a\u0443\u043c\u0430 \u041d\u0438\u0441\u0438\u043c\u0443\u0440\u043