imura/398191}}</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center\"\n|+ Appearances and goals by club, season and competition\n|-\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Club\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Season\n!colspan=\"3\"|League\n!colspan=\"2\"|National Cup\n!colspan=\"2\"|League Cup\n!colspan=\"2\"|Continental\n!colspan=\"2\"|Other\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n|-\n!Division!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals\n|-\n|rowspan=\"5\"|[[Vegalta Sendai]]\n|[[2015 J1 League|2015]]\n|rowspan=\"4\"|[[J1 League]]\n|0||0||0||0||1||0||colspan=\"2\"|-||colspan=\"2\"|-||1||0\n|-\n|[[2016 J1 League|2016]]\n|12||1||0||0||2||0||colspan=\"2\"|-||colspan=\"2\"|-||14||1\n|-\n|[[2017 J1 League|2017]]\n|28||2||0||0||10||2||colspan=\"2\"|-||colspan=\"2\"|-||38||4\n|-\n|[[2018 J1 League|2018]]\n|24||11||1||0||5||2||colspan=\"2\"|-||colspan=\"2\"|-||30||13\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n!64!!14!!1!!0!!18!!4!!-!!-!!-!!-!!83!!18\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\"|[[PFC CSKA Moscow|CSKA Moscow]]\n|[[2018\u201319 PFC CSKA Moscow season|2018\u201319]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[Russian Premier League|RPL]]\n|12||2||1||0||colspan=\"2\"|-||2||0||0||0||15||2\n|-\n|[[2019\u201320 PFC CSKA Moscow season|2019\u201320]]\n|5||0||2||2||colspan=\"2\"|-||1||0||colspan=\"2\"|-||8||2\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n!17!!2!!3!!2!!-!!-!!3!!0!!0!!0!!23!!4\n|-\n|[[Portimonense S.C.|Portimonense]] (loan)\n|[[2019\u201320 Primeira Liga|2019\u201320]]\n|[[Primeira Liga]]\n|2||0||0||0||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|-||colspan=\"2\"|-||2||0\n|-\n!colspan=\"3\"|Career total\n!83!!16!!4!!2!!18!!4!!3!!0!!-!!-!!108!!22\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.vegalta.co.jp/topteam/profile_top/player30.html Profile at Vegalta Sendai]\n*{{J.League player|15808}}\n\n{{Portimonense S.C. squad}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Nishimura, Takuma}}\n[[Category:1996 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Association football people from Aichi Prefecture]]\n[[Category:Japanese footballers]]\n[[Category:J1 League players]]\n[[Category:J3 